  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discover Timeline Traveler II</h1><p></p><br><h1>Join Our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description: </strong></h2><br>Timeline Traveler is a puzzle game that combined time control and platformer element together to provide a new game experience. In the game, you need to control the timelines and change the moving timing of objects in the scene to help the hero reach the goal!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay: </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Observe the Scene</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/bb60d8fe36c37cb9670d9c34e2be4eac.poster.avif?t=1602281771\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/bb60d8fe36c37cb9670d9c34e2be4eac.webm?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/bb60d8fe36c37cb9670d9c34e2be4eac.mp4?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The objects on the scene will act according to the timelines. You may observe how is the movement of those object.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage the Timelines</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/fdd40ad9cf5000d927397ecef7cde2c9.poster.avif?t=1602281771\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/fdd40ad9cf5000d927397ecef7cde2c9.webm?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/fdd40ad9cf5000d927397ecef7cde2c9.mp4?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>By moving the timelines, the moving timing of the objects will also change.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach the Goal</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/d3164561b129aac2ad1aa1fa7419108b.poster.avif?t=1602281771\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/d3164561b129aac2ad1aa1fa7419108b.webm?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417960/extras/d3164561b129aac2ad1aa1fa7419108b.mp4?t=1602281771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Try to help the Clock Monster to reach the goal and finish the level!",
